name: heart blob X
description: "heart blob X, 2021" is the digital redux of the analog work, "heart blob, 2018". It is from a series of artworks entitled 'Heart Blob' of which this is a fragmented resection of the original and namesake of the whole series. The original work is made with materials collected from walls in Los Angeles, Brooklyn & Madrid. 'heart blob,2018' was exhibited in 2019 as part of an installation commissioned by the the I.C.M.A. and E.P.A (Environmental Protection Agency). All artwork, digital manipulation and soundscape by codyfied.
